<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="off-prep">off <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɒf/    美 /ɔːf/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>从…离开；从…移开：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Can you get the lid off this box?
你能把这个盒子的盖子打开吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>离；距；偏离：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The ship sank 10 miles off the coast.
那艘船在离海岸10英里处沉没了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There’s a small bathroom off the main bedroom.
有一个小浴室与主卧相连。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(因病等) 不工作；不上学：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I got off work at 10.
我10点钟下班。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>从…减掉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>50 percent off the price
5折的价格</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The Well Hotel stands in a quiet place <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the main road at the far end of the lake.  （2012 辽宁改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. off  </p></div>